{
  "script_id": "partial-derivative",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "想象你站在一片起伏的山坡上，脚下的高度随位置而变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "往东走会上坡还是下坡？往北走呢？坡有多陡？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "要回答这些问题，我们需要多元函数的变化率工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "partial-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/partial-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 3.62,
      "size": 57888,
      "text": "把高度看成函数 f(x, y)，只让 x 变、y 不动，得到沿东西方向的坡度，这是对 x 的偏导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "partial-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/partial-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "只让 y 变、x 不动，得到沿南北方向的坡度，这是对 y 的偏导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "partial-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/partial-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "每个偏导数，都是把另一个变量当常数后的普通导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "gradient",
      "line_id": "grad-1",
      "filename": "gradient-grad-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/gradient-grad-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "把两个偏导数拼成一个向量，就是梯度，记作 [fx, fy]。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "gradient",
      "line_id": "grad-2",
      "filename": "gradient-grad-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/gradient-grad-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "梯度既有方向又有大小，它的模长就是当地最陡的坡度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "gradient",
      "line_id": "grad-3",
      "filename": "gradient-grad-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/gradient-grad-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "图上白色箭头，正是每一点的梯度向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "steepest",
      "line_id": "steep-1",
      "filename": "steepest-steep-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/steepest-steep-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "奇妙的是，梯度永远垂直于等高线，也就是等高的那圈曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "steepest",
      "line_id": "steep-2",
      "filename": "steepest-steep-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/steepest-steep-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.67,
      "size": 42768,
      "text": "沿梯度方向上升最快，反方向下降最快，横切等高线则不升不降。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "在图上点击不同位置，观察箭头方向与长短如何随地形改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "试试碗、鞍面和波纹，感受梯度在山谷、山脊处的不同表现。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "偏导数量出沿单一方向的坡度，两者合成梯度向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "梯度垂直等高线，指向上升最陡的方向，模长就是坡度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-derivative",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-derivative/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "掌握了梯度，你就有了导航高维地形的指南针，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
